تدبیر میرے عشق کی کیا فائدہ طبیب
اب جان ہئ کے ساتھ یہ آزار جائے گا 

'Manat Murad' is a script I read right after 'Khuda aur Mohabbat.' I instantly felt a connection with the characters, their emotions, and journey. But then 'Ishq Jalebi' happened, followed by 'Chaudhary and Sons.' All these years, Manat Siddique & Chaudhary Murad were with me. I kept imagining the faces, thinking about the combination of actors and their on-screen chemistry. The script demanded enthusiasm and conviction (which is actually rare to find these days🙂)

In October 2022, we got on board @iiqraaz as Manat & @talha_chahour as Murad. (I think the script was waiting for them).

So here it is❗️ You guys are going to watch it tonight. I hope you like it as much as I loved doing it.

All of this couldn't have been possible without @abdullah.kadwani & @asadaqureshi. The producers everyone wants to work with because of their vision and hard work. My association with them is not an untold story. The opportunity, freedom & support they gave me in every project is unmatched. May Allah strengthen our bond with love and respect. I am also looking forward to my collaborations with them in the future.

'Manat Murad' is a @7thskyentertainment production written by talented @nadiaakhtar & you can watch it on @harpalgeotv every Monday and Tuesday at 8 pm."

Good luck to every member of my cast and crew

إِنَّا لِلَّهِ وَإِنَّآ إِلَيْهِ رَٰجِعُونَ
آپ کی یاد ھمیشہ خوشگوار احساس بن کر دل میں رہے گئ۔ اللہ تعالٰی آگے کی منزلیں آسان کرئیں۔ آمين

۔
آج محمد قوی خان صاحب بھی بہت یاد آے۔ قوی صاحب کے جانے کے بعد  میں نے بٹ صاحب کو پروفیشنلزم اور اداکاری کی یکساں بلندی پر دیکھا۔ آج کے بعد یہ الفاظ بھی جیسے کتابوں میں دفن ھو گے۔ اللہ دونوں کو جنت میں اعلی مقام عطا فرمائے۔ آمين 
عشق جلیلی کے باو جی ❤️ اور خئ کے دراب خان ❤️
